did apologize for slavery,

21:02.080 --> 21:04.710
but with the following caveat.

21:04.710 --> 21:07.960
"Disclaimer --
Nothing in this resolution,

21:07.960 --> 21:09.880
(A), authorizes or supports

21:09.880 --> 21:12.580
any claim
against the United States,

21:12.580 --> 21:15.000
or, (B), serves as a settlement

